Because of the rules of her thief family,

18
00:01:44,904 --> 00:01:47,340
she's going to be forced to
marry a guy she hates.

19
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:49,075
In order to refuse, she asked
you to be her lover.

20
00:01:49,075 --> 00:01:51,177
I have to compete with my thieving skills
against Takashi, who's a hypnotist.

21
00:01:51,177 --> 00:01:53,546
I'm in trouble!

22
00:01:53,546 --> 00:01:59,152
I was hypnotized by him and my mokkori
power was taken hostage.

23
00:01:59,152 --> 00:02:02,055
Ryo without mokkori power, oh, no.

24
