What? Is it stuck or something?

153
00:11:06,165 --> 00:11:07,733
Ryo!

154
00:11:07,733 --> 00:11:10,970
Hold me! Please!

155
00:11:10,970 --> 00:11:12,437
What?

156
00:11:14,006 --> 00:11:15,473
Ryo!

157
00:11:15,841 --> 00:11:19,368
Damn, this must be Takashi's trap
in order to stop me here.

158
00:11:26,552 --> 00:11:28,543
What are you talking about?!

159
00:11:28,921 --> 00:11:30,445
Hurry!

160
00:11:31,357 --> 00:11:35,657
Oh, no, I can't take my eyes off her!

161
00:11:43,569 --> 00:11:46,629
Mokkori, mokkori, powerful mokkori!

162
00:11:46,806 --> 00:11:47,773
Kasumi!

163
00:11:49,375 --> 00:11:52,071
Mr. Saeba, your mokkori is back, isn't it?!

164
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:56,177
Yes, because of you!

165
00:11:57,416 --> 00:11:59,585
What am I doing like this?!

166
00:11:59,585 --> 00:12:03,214
I guess you were put into
a state of hypnosis,

167
00:12:03,656 --> 00:12:06,989
so that when you saw the mirror,
you would start tempting me.

168
00:12:07,426 --> 00:12:10,327
But because of that, my mokkori is back!

169
00:12:11,564 --> 00:12:12,861
Where did the mirror go?!

170
00:12:15,267 --> 00:12:18,566
I didn't expect that, but my
goal is accomplished.

171
00:12:19,271 --> 00:12:21,034
I have the mirror!

172
00:12:25,678 --> 00:12:29,580
I got you twice with the same trick.
Now, Kasumi is mine!

173
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:33,082
Wait, you coward!

174
00:12:34,987 --> 00:12:36,454
What is it, Mr. Saeba?

175
00:12:36,889 --> 00:12:40,092
I can get the mirror back now! Let me go!

176
00:12:40,092 --> 00:12:41,753
You don't need to.

177
00:12:46,265 --> 00:12:48,927
Oh, no, the resident heard us.

178
00:12:49,735 --> 00:12:51,370
Go without me.

179
00:12:51,370 --> 00:12:53,305
I have something to do here.

180
00:12:53,305 --> 00:12:55,207
What are you going to do?

181
00:12:55,207 --> 00:12:56,642
You might be caught!

182
00:12:56,642 --> 00:12:58,110
Don't worry.

183
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,977
Please try to gain time until
I get back. Later.

184
00:13:04,517 --> 00:13:05,745
Mr. Saeba?

185
00:13:20,466 --> 00:13:23,969
I wonder if he was caught or if he ran away?

186
00:13:23,969 --> 00:13:26,802
Great Aunt, I think it's useless
to wait for him any longer.

187
00:13:27,206 --> 00:13:30,073
Please admit that I have won this game.

188
00:13:30,709 --> 00:13:32,344
What are you talking about?!

189
00:13:32,344 --> 00:13:34,880
He got the mirror faster than you,

190
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:37,583
but you used cowardly hypnotism
and snatched it!

191
00:13:37,583 --> 00:13:39,051
Sure I did.

192
00:13:39,051 --> 00:13:44,123
But you knew about it, so it was
your mistake not to plan for it.

193
00:13:44,123 --> 00:13:45,488
What the hell?!

194
00:13:45,858 --> 00:13:47,985
He's right, Kasumi.

195
00:13:49,161 --> 00:13:52,631
Okay, I consider that Saeba
gave up the game.

196
00:13:52,631 --> 00:13:54,800
Now, I'll give you my judgment.

197
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:56,267
Wait!

198
00:13:57,069 --> 00:13:58,798
Hi, how are you doing?

199
00:13:59,538 --> 00:14:00,903
Mr. Saeba!

200
00:14:02,474 --> 00:14:05,311
What on earth were you doing until now?!

201
00:14:05,311 --> 00:14:07,613
Calm down. Don't worry.

202
00:14:07,613 --> 00:14:10,878
This game has been won by me.

203
00:14:11,617 --> 00:14:15,917
What? What are you talking about, after
you came back here late like this?!

204
00:14:16,722 --> 00:14:19,657
You think you won? What do you mean?

205
00:14:20,659 --> 00:14:25,323
After all, this was not a simple
competition of stealing skills.

206
00:14:26,832 --> 00:14:27,958
What?!

207
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,929
Well, before my explanation,

208
00:14:31,737 --> 00:14:33,227
I want you to look at something.

209
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:36,475
Takashi, turn the mirror this way.

210
00:14:36,475 --> 00:14:37,533
What?

211
00:14:40,412 --> 00:14:42,648
That's enough! What do you want?!

212
00:14:42,648 --> 00:14:45,845
Look at the reflection of
this mirror on the wall.

213
