and letters or pictures will appear
only in the reflection.

224
00:15:27,259 --> 00:15:29,022
A mirror like this is called a magic mirror.

225
00:15:29,995 --> 00:15:32,293
But how do you know?

226
00:15:33,799 --> 00:15:35,266
Lightning.

227
00:15:36,135 --> 00:15:37,569
Before the game started,

228
00:15:37,569 --> 00:15:41,840
Grandma showed us the mirror and, just
then, the lightning reflected on the mirror

229
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,467
and I saw those same letters.

230
00:15:43,809 --> 00:15:47,446
Therefore, I thought this mirror was the same.

231
00:15:47,446 --> 00:15:49,815
Oh, at that moment, such a short time!

232
00:15:49,815 --> 00:15:51,339
He is good!

233
00:15:53,018 --> 00:15:58,422
So what? I won because I stole that
mirror and brought it here.

234
00:15:59,191 --> 00:16:00,681
You still don't get it?

235
00:16:01,126 --> 00:16:03,862
This is one of the old waka
from the Shika Wakashu.

236
00:16:03,862 --> 00:16:05,762
What? Waka?

237
00:16:08,567 --> 00:16:12,025
Se o hayami, iwa ni sekakaru takigawa no.

238
00:16:12,438 --> 00:16:14,998
Wakarete mo, sue ni, awan tozo omou.

239
00:16:17,309 --> 00:16:19,078
The stream runs very fast.

240
00:16:19,078 --> 00:16:22,247
The stream hits the rock and the stream
is divided into two streams.

241
00:16:22,247 --> 00:16:24,613
However, later, those two streams
combine into one again.


242
