her husband either.

266
00:17:54,973 --> 00:18:00,878
I was hired by Kasumi only to cancel
her engagement to Takashi.

267
00:18:01,246 --> 00:18:02,338
Mr. Saeba!

268
00:18:03,515 --> 00:18:05,350
And one more thing.

269
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:06,840
This magic mirror has a secret.

270
00:18:07,386 --> 00:18:10,856
This mirror is one of two which
were kept by two lovers

271
00:18:10,856 --> 00:18:13,092
who wished to meet again.

272
00:18:13,092 --> 00:18:16,289
I wonder why you have one of them?

273
00:18:17,162 --> 00:18:21,266
