276
00:18:30,876 --> 00:18:32,503
There is only one answer.

277
00:18:33,345 --> 00:18:34,646
A long time ago,

278
00:18:34,646 --> 00:18:37,877
you fell in love with someone who
was not a member of the family.

279
00:18:38,317 --> 00:18:41,854
However, because of the strict family rules,

280
00:18:41,854 --> 00:18:46,223
you and the owner of this mirror
had to be separated.

281
00:18:47,826 --> 00:18:52,490
I met a man in the house, who
woke up because of the noise.

282
00:18:54,266 --> 00:18:59,294
I'm sorry, but your man passed
away a long time ago.

283
00:18:59,938 --> 00:19:03,305
But he never forgot about
you until he died.

284
00:19:03,842 --> 00:19:08,711
He died holding this mirror
and calling your name.

285
00:19:10,415 --> 00:19:12,584
One more thing to add,

286
00:19:12,584 --> 00:19:15,521
the man I met there was adopted,

287
00:19:15,521 --> 00:19:21,323
so your lover didn't marry, because
he missed you too much.

288
00:19:39,311 --> 00:19:42,940
I thought that my tears had
dried up back then.

289
00:19:43,682 --> 00:19:45,617
He left a dying wish.

290
00:19:45,617 --> 00:19:48,554
He said that he hadn't been able
to see you while he was alive,

291
00:19:48,554 --> 00:19:51,022
but he wished that the mirror would
make its way back to you.

292
00:19:56,328 --> 00:19:59,786
I'm sorry if I reopened old wounds,

293
00:20:00,632 --> 00:20:03,795
but now, you've got your tears back,

294
00:20:04,303 --> 00:20:09,575
